      "para_id": "Q004939.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Urkugnuna , child of Lu-Ninŋirsu , the shepherd of the nakabtum , is your servant ."
